"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:12:18.000Z","msg":"班紅衛兵就繼續停留在口腔期，只要有著數，侵華日軍佢哋都會照奶鞋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9faf3023bb89d2ab828a7dc2def2e645e68ad44","tid":1270241,"uid":165339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14440d9e8df70e0bebc6b99e0bfd771c8bd1895","tid":1270241,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:13:43.000Z","msg":"想一想自己是二戰納粹裡的德國人如何反納粹"}]}